The field that you want to search must be indexed as MongoDB Vector Search
[autoEmbed](avs-types-auto-embed) type inside a
[index definition](avs-types-vector-search) index type.

A `$vectorSearch` pipeline has the following prototype form:

```javascript
{
  "$vectorSearch": {
    "exact": true | false,
    "filter": {<filter-specification>},
    "index": "<index-name>",
    "limit": <number-of-results>,
    "model": "<model-name>",
    "numCandidates": <number-of-candidates>,
    "path": "<field-to-search>",
    "query": {
      "text": "<query-text>"
    }
  }
}
```
